    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I would do like the hits widgets does: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/widgets/hits/defaultTemplates.js\n\nMostly because we will be able to get rid of the mighty webpack loaders that are a pain to handle and bad for portability to our users (i.e. using require(instantsearch.js))\n\nWith templatestrings and regular js files you are good I think. Those templates are really small.\n",
