    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "With template strings it's really easy to do templates multiline. It does not depend on any module loader, we are compatible with any JavaScript environment.\n\nWebpack loaders/browserify transforms are cool hacks but then you are tied to the module loader.\n",
